Azure Text-to-Speech (TTS) Notice

Some audio assets in this repository were generated using Microsoft Azure AI Speech (Text-to-Speech) with a paid Standard (S0 / Pay-As-You-Go) resource.

Usage Rights:
- Audio, which is produced with a paid Azure Speech TTS resource, may be used in published or redistributed works, including commercial scenarios, subject to Microsoft’s Product Terms for Azure Speech services.

This project’s Creative Commons license applies to the content contained in this repository. It does not license or alter Microsoft Azure services themselves. Microsoft is not affiliated with, and does not endorse, this project.

If you redistribute or adapt the audio assets, you must:
1) comply with this project’s CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 terms (attribution, non-commercial, share-alike), and
2) ensure your use of Azure-generated audio remains consistent with Microsoft’s service terms applicable at the time of generation.

Attribution example:
“Includes audio generated with Microsoft Azure AI Speech (S0). Original project: <REPO_NAME or URL>. Licensed under CC BY-NC-SA 4.0.”
